Monday:go to the skool w/ Ryan and Jennifer to practice for the senior graduation cause there gonna be doing some stuff...
Tuesday:Supposedly were having a party for the hell of it...but I dont kno how thats gonna turn out...
Wednesday:IDK
Thursday:IDK
Friday:go to the senior graduation...and see my whore Jonathon graduate:)Im proud of you biotch!!!!!!
and thats it....
Until next time...Buh Bye...
~SARAH~
